{"483980":{"success":true,"data":{"type":"game","name":"Mad Father《狂父》","steam_appid":483980,"required_age":0,"is_free":false,"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/483980\/extras\/MadfatherSteam.png?t=1735191803\" \/><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/483980\/extras\/AboutGame_JP2.png?t=1735191803\" \/><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">《狂父》是由日本むぎせん玩家制作的恐怖解密类单机游戏。<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">我们可以操纵女主角阿雅(アヤ)，在大豪宅里阿雅去拯救爸爸途中会遇上各种难题。<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/483980\/extras\/Cast_JP.png?t=1735191803\" \/><\/p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> 阿雅<\/h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">本作的女主角。隐约知道父亲进行可怕实验但不肯面对现实的女孩。<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/483980\/extras\/Cast_Aya.png?t=1735191803\" \/><\/p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">父亲<\/h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">阿雅的父亲。在大豪宅的地下室内进行可怕的实验活动。<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/483980\/extras\/Cast_Father.png?t=1735191803\" \/><\/p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">母亲<\/h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">阿雅的母亲。在游戏开始时的一年前就已经去世了，深爱着阿雅父亲，并且真相是……(在取得她写给阿雅的父亲情信中可以了解到)<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/483980\/extras\/Cast_Mother.png?t=1735191803\" \/><\/p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> 玛莉亚<\/h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">以阿雅父亲的助手及情人的身分，<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">居住在这个家里的女仆。<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/483980\/extras\/Cast_Maria.png?t=1735191803\" \/><\/p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> 谜之黑衣人<\/h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">经常在故事中突然出现并帮助阿雅，自称推销员。<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">收集了所有宝石後在IF剧情中知道其真正目的。<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/483980\/extras\/Cast_Orge.png?t=1735191803\" \/><\/p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> 金髪的少年<\/h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">协助阿雅离开大屋的谜之少年。<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/483980\/extras\/Cast_Boy.png?t=1735191803\" \/><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/483980\/extras\/System_JP.png?t=1735191803\" \/><\/p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> 电锯<\/h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">可将木材等破坏。<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><\/p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">暗号笔记<\/h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">根据笔记的提示可打开密码锁。<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><\/p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">宝石<\/h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">重要物品。隐藏於大屋各处。如收集所有宝石的话……？<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><\/p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">结局<\/h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">共有3个结局，其中一个为官方设定的真正结局。<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">在完成结局後，再重新多玩一遍游戏，将会看到爸爸及妈妈所写的日记，以及妈妈写给爸爸的情信。<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <\/p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">僵尸<\/h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">袭击阿雅的僵尸，是阿雅的父亲在实验中的亡魂。<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">请注意持有武器的僵尸，被捉住的话随时被杀。<\/p>","about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/483980\/extras\/MadfatherSteam.png?t=1735191803\" \/><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/483980\/extras\/AboutGame_JP2.png?t=1735191803\" \/><\/p